segment.source: Importing your file overwrites everything that’s currently in the tool, so make sure it’s what you really mean to do.

segment.source: On the File menu of the Enterprise Mode Site List Manager, click Import.
segment.target: On the File menu of the Enterprise Mode Site List Manager, click Import.

segment.source: Go to your exported .EMIE file (for example, ), and then click Open.
segment.target: Go to your exported .EMIE file (for example, ), and then click Open.

segment.source: Review the alert message about all of your entries being overwritten.
segment.target: Review the alert message about all of your entries being overwritten.

segment.source: If you still want to import the file, click Yes.
segment.target: If you still want to import the file, click Yes.
